        {
            "title": "油價飆升引發華爾街拋售後美股期貨持穩",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkT.J6EQ.Cm0QnT5ytAxjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7306L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 美國股指期貨週四晚間幾乎持平,此前華爾街當日延續跌勢,投資者在中東局勢升級和油價飆升的背景下保持謹慎,同時等待美國關鍵就業報告出爐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:S&amp;P 500期貨;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://in.investing.com/indices/us-spx-500-futures?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">S&amp;P 500期貨</a>小幅上漲0.1%至6,843.50點,納斯達克100指數期貨上漲0.1%至25,072.75點,截至美國東部時間20:10(格林威治標準時間00:10)。道指期貨上漲0.2%至48,064.0點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/><br/></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>油價飆升拖累華爾街下跌</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華爾街主要指數週四收低,延續本週更廣泛的跌勢,地緣政治風險和能源價格上漲削弱了風險偏好。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-61fd2f3b-39b5-3051-926c-2c3fc5a6a447-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道瓊工業平均指數下跌1.6%,S&amp;P 500指數下跌0.6%,納斯達克綜合指數收跌0.3%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價在盤中大幅跳漲,隨著中東局勢加劇以及對波斯灣航運路線的擔憂加劇,原油價格飆升逾8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價飆升加劇了通脹擔憂並拖累股市,尤其是對利率敏感的成長股。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">能源價格上漲往往會壓縮企業利潤率和消費者支出,同時也使聯準會控制通脹的努力變得更加複雜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">地緣政治緊張局勢也推動投資者轉向更安全的資產,導致本週全球金融市場波動加劇。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>週五將公布就業數據</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場參與者目前正在等待週五公布的2月份美國非農就業報告,該報告可能為勞動力市場健康狀況和貨幣政策前景提供新的信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟學家預計美國經濟在2月份新增約5.8萬個就業崗位,此前上月的數據強於預期,而失業率預計將保持在4.3%附近。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就業報告預計將在塑造市場對聯準會今年降息預期方面發揮關鍵作用。強勁的勞動力市場可能使政策制定者有空間將利率維持在較高水平更長時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易員目前預計聯準會將在今年稍後開始放寬政策,儘管近期經濟韌性和地緣政治風險已經削弱了對激進降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE%E5%BE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E6%8C%81%E7%A9%A9-015328775.html",
